t", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Validates and decodes the JWT token\nToken checked for\n\n> - signature of JWT token\n> - token issued date is valid\n\n```\nparam token\n\njwt token\n\nparam secret\n\nclient specific secret\n\nreturn boolean\n\nTrue if valid token, False otherwise\n\nraises TokenIssuerError\n\nif iss field not present\n\nraises TokenIssuedAtError\n\nif iat field not present\n\nraises TokenExpiredError\n\nIf the iat value expires this token\n\nraises TokenDecodeError\n\nIf the token cannot be decoded because it failed validation\n\nraises TokenAlgorithmError\n\nIf the algorithm is not recognised\n\nraises TokenError\n\nIf any other type of jwt exception is raised when trying jwt.decode\n```\n"]}, {"name": "notifications_python_client.authentication.validate_jwt_token", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "decoded_token", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "notifications_python_client.authentication.decode_token", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "token", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Decode token but don;t check the signature\n\\:param token:\n\\:return decoded token:\n"]}, {"name": "notifications_python_client.authentication.epoch_seconds", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "notifications_python_client.authentication.__algorithm__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "notifications_python_client.authentication.__type__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "notifications_python_client.authentication.__bound__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "notifications_python_client.authentication.INVALID_FUTURE_TOKEN_ERROR_MESSAGE", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}]}